text="Breaking changes">Breaking changes</fr:title></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p><fr:link
href="jms-00CW.xml"
title="Forester 3.0"
addr="jms-00CW"
type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> introduces a number of breaking changes to the source language in order to facilitate maintainability, diagnostic support, and extensibility of both the <fr:link
